snippet.title: Frozen Adventures Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Adventure through the World of Disney's Frozen in an all-new mobile match-3 puzzle and decorate game! Join Elsa, Anna and Olaf as you solve puzzles, collect rewards and make choices to build and design the Kingdom of Arendelle and beyond!

❄️❄️Pre-register for a FREE in-game gift! ❄️❄️

Subscribe to Frozen Adventures: https://jamcity.me/FA_PreReg_YT
Like our official Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/frozenadventuresgame/?ref=bookmarks
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/frozenadventuresgame/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/frozenadvgame

Frozen Adventures will be coming to Google Play and App Store in November 2019.
